.sheet-XP
	input.sheet-SkinCheck(type='hidden', name='attr_SkinCheck', value='0')
	.sheet-Subsection
		span(data-i18n='experience') Experience
	.sheet-NoElemental
		p(align='center')
			input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_XP1')
			span.sheet-altbox
			input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_XP2')
			span.sheet-altbox
			input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_XP3')
			span.sheet-altbox
			input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_XP4')
			span.sheet-altbox
			input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_XP5')
			span.sheet-altbox
	.sheet-Elemental
		p(align='center')
			input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_XP1')
			span.sheet-altbox
			input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_XP2')
			span.sheet-altbox
			input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_XP3')
			span.sheet-altbox
			input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_XP4')
			span.sheet-altbox
			input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_XP5')
			span.sheet-altbox
			| &nbsp;
			input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_XP6')
			span.sheet-altbox
			input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_XP7')
			span.sheet-altbox
			input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_XP8')
			span.sheet-altbox
			input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_XP9')
			span.sheet-altbox
			input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_XP10')
			span.sheet-altbox

	.sheet-NoSurvivor.sheet-NoElemental
		input.sheet-checkbox.sheet-ExpToggle(type='checkbox', name='attr_Toggle-XP-Instructions', value='1', checked='')
		span.sheet-anglebox
		|  
		span.sheet-ExpHeader
			span(data-i18n='instructions') Instructions
		.sheet-Expander
			span(data-i18n='experience-description')
				| Mark 
				i Experience
				|  when a roll totals 6 or less; or when a move tells you to do so
			| . 
			span(data-i18n='xp-description')
				| Once you have filled all 5 boxes, uncheck them and choose an 
				i Improvement
				|  option
			| .
	.sheet-Elemental
		input.sheet-checkbox.sheet-ExpToggle(type='checkbox', name='attr_Toggle-XP-Instructions', value='1', checked='')
		span.sheet-anglebox
		|  
		span.sheet-ExpHeader
			span(data-i18n='instructions') Instructions
		.sheet-Expander
			+t("Mark Experience when a roll totals 6 or less; or when a move tells you to do so.")
			+t("Once you have filled all ten boxes, uncheck them and choose an improvement.")
	.sheet-Survivor
		input.sheet-checkbox.sheet-ExpToggle(type='checkbox', name='attr_Toggle-XP-Instructions', value='1', checked='')
		span.sheet-anglebox
		|  
		span.sheet-ExpHeader
			span(data-i18n='instructions') Instructions
		.sheet-Expander
			+translate('Mark an experience box whenever:<ul><li>You roll for a move.<li>You roll a 6 or less on a move (in addition to the mark for rolling a move).<li>You suffer harm.<li>Something else tells you to.</ul>')
	.sheet-Display-Only-Narrow
		include survivor-leveling.pug
		include improvements.pug
